Name: Tay Do Café Still the best

Content.summary: 'Tay Do Café Still the best' - a blog post by Darren Ferguson about Tay Do Café, food written on 06 August 2006
Content.tags: Tay Do Café, food, Vietnamese, Bun Bo Hue
Content.bodyText: Paid a return visit to the wonderful Tay Do Café this weekend. It is the only place we ever rated with five chillis, and I am pleased to say that it is still just as good. We got a better picture of the food too.
